<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <link rel="icon" href="../static/img/newfavicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <title><%= page_title %> - Artemis Store</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --app-bg: #f5f7fb;
            --sidebar-bg: #101827;
            --sidebar-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            --sidebar-hover: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            --sidebar-text: #eef2ff;
            --sidebar-muted: #9ca3af;
            --accent: #2563eb;
            --content-text: #111827;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            user-select: none;
            background: var(--app-bg);
            color: var(--content-text);
            font-family: "Segoe UI", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
        }

        .app-shell {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
        }

        .sidebar {
            width: 250px;
            height: 100vh;
            position: fixed;
            inset: 0 auto 0 0;
            background: var(--sidebar-bg);
            color: var(--sidebar-text);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            padding: 18px 14px;
            border-right: 1px solid var(--sidebar-border);
        }

        .brand {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            padding: 8px 8px 20px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--sidebar-border);
        }

        .brand img {
            width: 42px;
            height: 42px;
            object-fit: contain;
        }

        .brand-title {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 1.34rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            line-height: 1.1;
        }

        .sidebar-nav {
            display: grid;
            gap: 5px;
        }

        .sidebar a {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            min-height: 42px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--sidebar-text);
            padding: 9px 10px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            transition: background-color 0.16s ease, color 0.16s ease, transform 0.16s ease;
        }

        .sidebar a:hover {
            background: var(--sidebar-hover);
            color: #ffffff;
            transform: translateX(2px);
        }

        .nav-icon {
            width: 26px;
            height: 26px;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            flex: 0 0 26px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.14);
            color: #bfdbfe;
        }

        .nav-icon svg {
            width: 16px;
            height: 16px;
            stroke: currentColor;
            stroke-width: 2;
            fill: none;
            stroke-linecap: round;
            stroke-linejoin: round;
        }

        .sidebar-footer {
            margin-top: auto;
            padding-top: 14px;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--sidebar-border);
            color: var(--sidebar-muted);
            font-size: 0.82rem;
        }

        .sidebar-footer a {
            min-height: 34px;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .version-text {
            margin: 10px 4px 0;
            color: var(--sidebar-muted);
            line-height: 1.35;
        }

        .main-content {
            width: calc(100% - 250px);
            margin-left: 250px;
            padding: 28px 30px 40px;
        }

        .page-heading {
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            padding: 18px 20px;
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.04);
        }

        .page-heading h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 1.75rem;
            font-weight: 750;
        }

        .page-heading p {
            margin: 6px 0 0;
            color: #6b7280;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 100%;
        }

        @media (max-width: 820px) {
            .sidebar {
                width: 220px;
            }

            .main-content {
                width: calc(100% - 220px);
                margin-left: 220px;
                padding: 22px 18px 34px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="app-shell">
        <aside class="sidebar">
            <div class="brand">
                <img src="../static/img/newlogorbg.png" alt="ArtemisStore">
                <p class="brand-title">ArtemisStore</p>
            </div>

            <nav class="sidebar-nav">
                <a href="#" id="applicationsLink"><span class="nav-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="3" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="14" y="3" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="3" y="14" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="14" y="14" width="7" height="7"/></svg></span><span>Applications</span></a>
                <a href="#" id="winofficeLink"><span class="nav-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M4 5h16v11H4z"/><path d="M8 20h8"/><path d="M12 16v4"/></svg></span><span>Windows et Office</span></a>
                <a href="#" id="updatesLink"><span class="nav-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-2.64-6.36"/><path d="M21 3v6h-6"/></svg></span><span>Mises a jour</span></a>
                <a href="#" id="WinOptimisationsLink"><span class="nav-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M13 2L4 14h7l-1 8 9-12h-7z"/></svg></span><span>Optimisation</span></a>
                <a href="#" id="IntegrityLink"><span class="nav-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 3l8 4v6c0 5-3.4 7.6-8 9-4.6-1.4-8-4-8-9V7z"/><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/></svg></span><span>Integrite</span></a>
                <a href="#" id="settingsLink"><span class="nav-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path d="M19.4 15a1.8 1.8 0 0 0 .3 2l.1.1-2.1 2.1-.1-.1a1.8 1.8 0 0 0-2-.3 1.8 1.8 0 0 0-1 1.6V21h-3v-.6a1.8 1.8 0 0 0-1-1.6 1.8 1.8 0 0 0-2 .3l-.1.1-2.1-2.1.1-.1a1.8 1.8 0 0 0 .3-2 1.8 1.8 0 0 0-1.6-1H4v-3h.6a1.8 1.8 0 0 0 1.6-1 1.8 1.8 0 0 0-.3-2l-.1-.1 2.1-2.1.1.1a1.8 1.8 0 0 0 2 .3 1.8 1.8 0 0 0 1-1.6V3h3v.6a1.8 1.8 0 0 0 1 1.6 1.8 1.8 0 0 0 2-.3l.1-.1 2.1 2.1-.1.1a1.8 1.8 0 0 0-.3 2 1.8 1.8 0 0 0 1.6 1h.6v3h-.6a1.8 1.8 0 0 0-1.6 1z"/></svg></span><span>Parametres</span></a>
            </nav>

            <div class="sidebar-footer">
                <a href="#" id="openLogBtn"><span class="nav-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M4 4h16v16H4z"/><path d="M8 8h8"/><path d="M8 12h8"/><path d="M8 16h5"/></svg></span><span>Logs</span></a>
                <a href="<%= githubLink %>" id="githubExternalLink"><span class="nav-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 19c-5 1.5-5-2.5-7-3m14 6v-3.9a3.4 3.4 0 0 0-1-2.6c3.2-.4 6.5-1.6 6.5-7A5.4 5.4 0 0 0 20 4a5 5 0 0 0-.1-3s-1.2-.4-3.9 1.5A13.4 13.4 0 0 0 12 2c-1.4 0-2.7.2-4 .6C5.3.6 4.1 1 4.1 1A5 5 0 0 0 4 4a5.4 5.4 0 0 0-1.5 3.8c0 5.3 3.3 6.5 6.4 6.9a3.4 3.4 0 0 0-1 2.6V22"/></svg></span><span>GitHub</span></a>
                <p class="version-text">Version <%= version %><br>By <%= author %></p>
            </div>
        </aside>

        <main class="main-content">
            <div class="page-heading">
                <h1><%= page_title %></h1>
                <p>Gerez vos applications, mises a jour et outils Windows depuis un seul endroit.</p>
            </div>
